  "summary": "Malicious code in @corpweb-ui/wmkt-library (npm)",
  "details": "Supply-chain attack. Package @corpweb-ui/wmkt-library@99.99.11 contains a preinstall hook that executes system commands (id, pwd, hostname) via child_process.exec and exfiltrates the output to a Telegram bot (token [redacted-credential], chatId 1483949647). The code explicitly states \"RCE CONFIRMED\" and targets the package itself. Version 99.99.11 suggests typosquatting/impersonation. This is a clear data exfiltration attack via npm lifecycle hook.",
